Wanitwa Mos:
Wanitwa Mos have 7 songs on the Spotify Top 200 Weekly South Africa chart. 
 They first appeared on the chart on 2021-12-23. Their most recent appearance has been on 2024-02-29. They have a total of 19689091 million streams. 
. His highest position on the chart is 1 for the song Sofa Silahlane which was at this position on 2022-05-26
 The songs of his that have appeared on the chart are Dali Nguwe ... Keneilwe (feat. Dalom Kids) ... Kuwe ... Makhelwane (feat. Casswell P) ... Sofa Silahlane ... Thando ... Uthando
